{"tid":1736190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【分化注意】不要說「搞到手足送頭」，試著說「死魔警濫捕死全家」","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:06:12.000Z","uid":165018,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ab574dfea6393369d70e472426abd6b4e2a804d7","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知大家見到理大入邊有手足投降好撚嬲，心入面想發洩<br />\n但係你依家屌理大手足有撚用咩，宜家俾人拉又係佢地，要上庭又係佢地，要坐十年都係佢地。<br />\n我地呢邊仲有時間上連登嘅人，真係有資格屌理大手足咩？佢地已經要背負好多野，從比人困住超過24小時，到依家18歲以下比人抄牌、18以上幾時被捕，唔撚通仲要承受你地班友加比佢地嘅罪惡感？<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁嬲，想發洩，麻煩你地對準翻政權、對準翻黑警魔警同佢地全家。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說「搞到手足送頭」，試著說「死魔警濫捕死全家」；<br />\n不要說「搞到手足送頭」，試著說「死魔警濫捕死全家」；<br />\n不要說「搞到手足送頭」，試著說「死魔警濫捕死全家」。<br />\n<br />\n從來不是因為理大手足比人困於是我地救，然後比人拉。<br />\n而係根本香港呢個地方，濫捕已經係好撚常見嘅野。</span></span>"},{"pid":"bdc1fb6fadb63550385e6486472418ef69e2ede1","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n仲係入面嘅手足，撐住。<br />\n出門仲有好多人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救</span></span>你地出黎<br />\n係救你地，唔係要你地自首"},{"pid":"460c66c664d36fb9194f7d72ef4502f1363fbc7c","tid":1736190,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1299c94d8488a7ae7e8bcddd1c675c803b788a97","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"我知好多未必真係分化撚，只不過恨鐵不成鋼所以先出黎講。<br />\n同大家一樣，理大手足一樣會重視尖東一帶為左救佢地而出黎嘅手足。<br />\n但係，有啲野，無需要我地再加把口落去，深化佢地已經有嘅傷口。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你估理大手足見到尖東手足比人拉，佢地會好開心咩？唔會架。</span></span><br />\n既然係大家都知道嘅事，點解我地要加把口落去繼續屌理大手足？你加深佢地嘅罪惡感，有幫助咩？"},{"pid":"df90f93b94c3f033b078fef503130275135df5ae","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"推啊啊啊<br />\n我知你地好撚嬲啊，但係唔好屌啊啊啊<br />\n依家見到你地放棄曬理大啲手足，對家好撚開心啊！！！"},{"pid":"0260149c36134925ca28e80a1610f39418593ec2","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"幫手推啊求下你地，唔好令到手足之間分化！！！"},{"pid":"8443128afd6b5347d0f9862c5e9e7c1974af2e69","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解越黎越多人出po屌理大，你地唔係咁都唔明啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"187c462d8ab2f41d9a7bbb1d767709351760f78d","tid":1736190,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"一入夜就好多五毛又出嚟分化同散佈失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40156838905b68e7e64e4490f618d4b7d952dba","tid":1736190,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"true，唔好分化，要煲大"},{"pid":"32fab5c5bb821668637fb7fcdb0d7b2e4f3f016f","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187c462d8ab2f41d9a7bbb1d767709351760f78d","tid":1736190,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"一入夜就好多五毛又出嚟分化同散佈失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好多人都因為情緒而俾佢地牽引住&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"376451b55b3ef298550115cfbd22f060392b883b","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"求下你地，幫手推<br />\n你覺得我大愛膠又好，左膠又好&hellip;&hellip;起碼你地內部勇武手足千奇唔可以分化&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"34db27979432f151a67154167511f6d52453e614","tid":1736190,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6475f743cbee9aa1179d111e0fde98eb0c574cbe","tid":1736190,"uid":94137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"大家都有壓力有苦衷<br />\n但必須明白我地要面對既一切壓抑黑暗既局面係邊個比我地既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係呢個仆街政府同佢既爪牙死黑警呀！！！<br />\n大家認清敵人<br />\n唔好內訌</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ac8a695452dcd99f9ca7d36dac511e292ec1f443","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"不割啊啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"4c2571f512d48072680b6c768d28f83b73f57386","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fcf8995a777ecb4796faef4eb92b319a73e034d3","tid":1736190,"uid":320142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"黑警濫捕先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef395ac5d5c6731763afc8083d04993b149ceaf","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"00800e3be6f58eb663d4f32105e9a443a8ba0ef7","tid":1736190,"uid":165018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"383738bc4bcf24fed2d028c93b52199682d1bd03","tid":1736190,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"岩 從來拉幾多人都係黑警話事"},{"pid":"abf821a7c5438e28b06837d58dd311acbb9a344a","tid":1736190,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"佢唔係警察<br />\n係武裝恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n佢無濫捕<br />\n無在大街虐殺香港市民"},{"pid":"aba0ae68268e97b260e2ac0ef1e396f5a298f964","tid":1736190,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike"